cu.explanation_en: Setting the SCTP input streams to an invalid value of 99 will cause SCTP association failures and prevent proper F1 interface communication with the DU.

du.explanation_en: Setting the 256QAM force off flag to an invalid value of 99 will cause modulation configuration errors and prevent proper downlink transmission setup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 256QAM 強制關閉旗標設定為無效值 99 會導致調製配置錯誤，並阻止正確的下行鏈路傳輸設定。
